That because of these false statements it avoided the payment of taxes and the
                    delivery of the corresponding royalty to the State defrauding the Government’s
                    interests in a manifest form;

That until the form in which the State will administer the oil fields and
                    refineries of the Standard Oil Company with all their annexes, fixtures,
                    machinery etc. is defined, they can be used by the Y. P. F. B.;
